profileText: a Representative from Arizona; born in Tucson, Pima County, Ariz., January 3, 1980; graduated from Cibola High School, Yuma, Ariz., 1998; attended Arizona Western College, Yuma, Ariz., 1999-2000; attended University of Arizona, Tucson, Ariz., 2000-2001; United States Navy, 2001-2014; writer; business owner; elected as a Republican to the One Hundred Eighteenth Congress (January 3, 2023-present).
